{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}],"title":"EditorUndoRedoManager","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot21EditorUndoRedoManagerC","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"EditorUndoRedoManager","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"EditorUndoRedoManager","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Class"},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/historyChanged","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/versionChanged"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/addDoMethod(object:method:_:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/addDoProperty(object:property:value:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/addDoReference(object:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/addUndoMethod(object:method:_:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/addUndoProperty(object:property:value:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/addUndoReference(object:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/commitAction(execute:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/createAction(name:mergeMode:customContext:backwardUndoOps:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/forceFixedHistory()","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/getHistoryUndoRedo(id:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/getObjectHistoryId(object:)","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/isCommittingAction()"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods","title":"Instance Methods","generated":true},{"title":"Type Properties","generated":true,"anchor":"Type-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/godotClassName"]},{"title":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/SpecialHistory"],"anchor":"Enumerations","generated":true}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Object"],"type":"inheritsFrom","kind":"relationships","title":"Inherits From"},{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SQ","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SH","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/s12IdentifiableP","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantRepresentable","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantStorable"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"EditorUndoRedoManager"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager","type":"reference"},{"text":" is a manager for ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/UndoRedo","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" objects associated with edited scenes. Each scene has its own undo history and "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager"},{"text":" ensures that each action performed in the editor gets associated with a proper scene. For actions not related to scenes (","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ProjectSettings","isActive":true},{"text":" edits, external resources, etc.), a separate global history is used.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The usage is mostly the same as ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/UndoRedo","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". You create and commit actions and the manager automatically decides under-the-hood what scenes it belongs to. The scene is deduced based on the first operation in an action, using the object from the operation. The rules are as follows:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the object is a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Node","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", use the currently edited scene;","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If the object is a built-in resource, use the scene from its path;","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the object is external resource or anything else, use global history.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This guessing can sometimes yield false results, so you can provide a custom context object when creating an action.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager","type":"reference"},{"text":" is intended to be used by Godot editor plugins. You can obtain it using ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorPlugin\/getUndoRedo()","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". For non-editor uses or plugins that don’t need to integrate with the editor’s undo history, use "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/UndoRedo","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The manager’s API is mostly the same as in "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/UndoRedo"},{"type":"text","text":", so you can refer to its documentation for more examples. The main difference is that "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" uses object + method name for actions, instead of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Callable","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This object emits the following signals:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/historyChanged","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/versionChanged"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/editorundoredomanager"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"Manages undo history of scenes opened in the editor.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/EditorUndoRedoManager/addUndoReference(object:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorUndoRedoManager\/addUndoReference(object:)","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Register a reference for “undo” that will be erased if the “undo” history is lost